      "created_at": "2022-06-04T21:38:00.065Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Eshte realitet i nje supermerkati ne Moske, arkiteture cariste qiellore e transformuar nga oligarki Putin ne supermarket toksor per te qerr paret e malazezve demokrate pa i kerkuar sqarim!<br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/joy.png?v=12\" title=\":joy:\" class=\"emoji only-emoji\" alt=\":joy:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-56683249\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-56683249\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">BBC News</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:800/450;\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/a/5/a59382df6ea212aed68798dcc50279ea0f775d5a_2_800x450.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/a/5/a59382df6ea212aed68798dcc50279ea0f775d5a_2_800x450.jpeg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/a/5/a59382df6ea212aed68798dcc50279ea0f775d5a.jpeg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/a/5/a59382df6ea212aed68798dcc50279ea0f775d5a.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/a/5/a59382df6ea212aed68798dcc50279ea0f775d5a_2_10x10.png\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-56683249\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Moscow's palatial Yeliseyevsky food hall closes after 120 years</a></h3>\n\n  <p>The iconic supermarket on Tverskaya Street in central Moscow first opened its doors 120 years ago.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
