      "created_at": "2022-06-16T06:58:08.195Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Perseu i pret koken Meduzës</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/8/b/8b21b6bf90d5bb4d592bafbd946188ac2aeff5e2.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/8b21b6bf90d5bb4d592bafbd946188ac2aeff5e2\" title=\"288658076_7813854581988617_1177161524068854571_n\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/8/b/8b21b6bf90d5bb4d592bafbd946188ac2aeff5e2_2_450x600.jpeg\" alt=\"288658076_7813854581988617_1177161524068854571_n\" data-base62-sha1=\"jQOBcq7vanZgHtjvRbDfR1DhRqW\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/8/b/8b21b6bf90d5bb4d592bafbd946188ac2aeff5e2_2_450x600.jpeg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/8/b/8b21b6bf90d5bb4d592bafbd946188ac2aeff5e2_2_675x900.jpeg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/8/b/8b21b6bf90d5bb4d592bafbd946188ac2aeff5e2_2_900x1200.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"604728\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">288658076_7813854581988617_1177161524068854571_n</span><span class=\"informations\">1080×1440 151 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Kokat ngjajne si dy pika uji: <strong>kush pret koka, pret kokën e vet.</strong></p>\n</blockquote>",
